  "description": "BobMode at 0.85 — deep in the storm surge. Full oscillator drift, heavy tape saturation, texture hiss, FX drowning in reverb. The sound of a synth pad recorded to cassette at 2 AM, played back through salt-damaged speakers. Lo-fi as an instrument, not a filter.",
